name: "Extreme Capitalism"- Illuminati Trials -visual story- 1/5 (All proceeds go to Helping Hand Project)
description: *They had a vision Less of US. WE had a vision NONE of them. When it came time to take what they had hoarded, what they had deprived of us for so long...
